ygData.messageBody:
Hehe I'm below lvl 20, so the trip is not for me (thou' I want the blacken
medallion, dunno what's tat buy sound very tempting for wiz, hehe).


Ziltus

On Friday, 02 July, 1999 7:15 PM, Gary Qui Hong Loong
[SMTP:kanglun@...] wrote:
> From: Gary Qui Hong Loong <kanglun@...>
>
> On the subject of camping for stuff, I'm proposing a trip to
Runnyeyes. The
> wiz can get the Blacken Medallion. The fighters type can get BI armors.
Monks
> and the rest can get pieces too to sell to ppl. Alot of ppl like BI armor
(the
> AC is worst and heavier than Banded stuff. Things ppl do for
fashion.......) but
> BI armor are magical so the only pieces I want is the gloves, boots and
the
> crown. The BI armor fits all races. and all fighter types can wear except
Monk
> (as usual). So u guys wanna come along this Sat? only lvl 20 and above.
The
> lower lvls will die very fast. And dangerous for 20plus too.
>
